verbose_text: For the measurement of chemokine levels, 220 muL of PRP or WP suspension supplemented with 1 mM CaCl 2 was stimulated with buffer (control), 15 mug/mL Pam3CSK4 diluted in PBS with 0.01% FCS, 15 mug/mL LPS, 10 muM TRAP-6, or 0.5 U/mL thrombin (positive control) for 30 minutes at room temperature.
